'''''Kibera Kid''''' ni filime ngufi yashyizwe mu gace ka Kibera i [[Nairobi]],  [[Kenya]] . Yanditswe, iyobowe kandi ifatanya na Nathan Collett ku bufatanye n’abaturage ba Kibera<ref>Kibera Kid (2006) | MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › kibera-kid</ref>. Iyi filime y'iminota cumi n'ibiri yagaragayemo abakinnyi ba filimi muri Kibera mubikorwa by'ingenzi<ref>The Theme Of Alienation In Selected Kenyan Films - UoN ... <nowiki>http://erepository.uonbi.ac.ke</nowiki> › handle</ref>. Yakinywe mu birori bya firime ku isi yose harimo iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Berlin <ref>Annual Archives | 2007 | Programme - Kibera Kid - | Berlinale | <nowiki>https://www.berlinale.de</nowiki> › archive › 02_programm_2007</ref>kandi yatsindiye [[:en:Student_EMMY|Student EMMY]] ukomoka muri Hollywood<ref>The Theme Of Alienation In Selected Kenyan Films - UoN ... <nowiki>http://erepository.uonbi.ac.ke</nowiki> › handle</ref> .  Byanditswe na BBC,  Reuters   hamwe na Al Jazeera Icyongereza<ref>Kibera Kid Film - African fashion Blog <nowiki>https://nairobifashionhub.co.ke</nowiki> › kibera-kid-film</ref> .  Muri Mata 2009, hafashwe amashusho yerekana amashusho ya Kibera Kid <ref>Filming in Hot Sun: Kenya, Kibera and the Power of the Image <nowiki>https://www.closeupfilmcentre.com</nowiki> › vertigo_magazine</ref>. Filime ndende yuzuye yibanda ku makimbirane ashingiye ku moko ndetse no kwiyunga. Iyi filime yagize ingaruka nini kuko yatumye hashyirwaho Hot Sun Foundation itoza urubyiruko rwo mucyaro gukora firime zabo<ref>Kibera kid (DVD video, 2006) [WorldCat.org] <nowiki>http://www.worldcat.org</nowiki> › oclc</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Kibera Kid ninkuru ya Otieno, impfubyi yimyaka 12 yo muri Kibera abana nitsinda ryabajura bagomba guhitamo ubuzima bw'agatsiko no gucungurwa. Inkuru ni ibihimbano ibintu  byerekanwe ntabwo ari ukuri<ref>Kibera Kid — Bongo Movie | Tanzania - BongoCinema.com <nowiki>http://www.bongocinema.com</nowiki> › movies_african › view</ref>. Ubugizi bwa nabi n'ubukene birasanzwe muri Kibera, nyamara hari benshi bazaharanira ubuzima bwiza nubwo ibintu bimeze nabi<ref>Kibera Kid (Short 2006) - IMDb <nowiki>https://www.imdb.com</nowiki> › title</ref>.
